      "totalCount": 2839,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025964&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5256&rangeEnd=5313",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d9432200813ab70a4g014cbc?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5256&rangeEnd=5313"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025964_5_895-954",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "895-954",
      "markText": "王战团说，礼貌是给俗人讲的，跟我免了。他又追了一句，王战团就是王战团，我娶了你大姑，不妨碍我还是我，我不是谁的大姑父。",
      "totalCount": 1764,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025964&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=895&rangeEnd=954",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d9432200813ab70a4g014cbc?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=895&rangeEnd=954"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025964_27_11817-11867",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "11817-11867",
      "markText": "王放说，我想你也走不了，年轻人。——吕旷闻见王放的酒味很重，又听见他说——有人把你种在这片土地上了。",
      "totalCount": 1440,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025964&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=11817&rangeEnd=11867",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d9432200813ab70a4g014cbc?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=11817&rangeEnd=11867"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025964_6_1563-1589",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1563-1589",
      "markText": "大姑说，看了就是真有病，不看就不一定有病，是个道理。",
      "totalCount": 1332,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025964&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1563&rangeEnd=1589",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d9432200813ab70a4g014cbc?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1563&rangeEnd=1589"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025964_5_1245-1304",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1245-1304",
      "markText": "王战团说，有本小说叫《海底两万里》，跟里面讲得一模一样，以前我也不信，书我回家找找，下次带给你。法国人写的，叫凡尔赛。",
      "totalCount": 1152,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025964&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1245&rangeEnd=1304",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d9432200813ab70a4g014cbc?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1245&rangeEnd=1304"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025964_7_2808-2875",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2808-2875",
      "markText": "王战团仍在上香，跟白三爷汇报日常，嘴里念着，我的思想问题已经深刻反省过，现在觉悟很高，随时可以登船。大姑说，你跟这拜政委呢？可闭嘴吧。",
      "totalCount": 816,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025964&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2808&rangeEnd=2875",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d9432200813ab70a4g014cbc?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2808&rangeEnd=2875"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025964_14_6351-6425",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "6351-6425",
      "markText": "有一台警车从村路上疾驰而过，好像是我俩特意给人家让路。孙尚全说，啥急事儿呢，出人命了？我说，抓非法集会的。孙尚全没回头问，你咋知道？我说，我报的警。",
      "totalCount": 816,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025964&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=6351&rangeEnd=6425",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d9432200813ab70a4g014cbc?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=6351&rangeEnd=6425"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025964_21_9299-9348",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "9299-9348",
      "markText": "在这片方圆两里的万家灯火间，幸福必须仰仗这声令人不寒而栗的号哭，方能维系它的名誉。幸福它配不上我。",
      "totalCount": 798,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025964&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=9299&rangeEnd=9348",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d9432200813ab70a4g014cbc?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=9299&rangeEnd=9348"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025964_7_1771-1862",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1771-1862",
      "markText": "王战团说，你看见那根天线没有，越往上越窄，你发现没？我说，咋了？王战团说，一辈子就是顺杆儿往上爬，爬到顶那天，你就是尖儿了。我问他，你爬到哪儿了？王战团说，我卡在节骨眼儿了，全是灰。",
      "totalCount": 754,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025964&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1771&rangeEnd=1862",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d9432200813ab70a4g014cbc?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1771&rangeEnd=1862"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025964_20_3267-3338",
